OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FThe decision to tighten eligibility
OL,7,Ffor Personal Independence Payments is
OL,8,Fprojected to affect around 800,000
OL,9,Fdisabled people. West of England
OL,10,FReporter Sangita Lal has the latest
OL,11,Ffrom Birmingham, and we hear from
OL,12,FDeputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,13,FAsthana from Westminster
OL,15,FChancellor Rachel Reeves confirmed
OL,16,Fhuge cuts to benefits in her Spring
OL,17,FStatement on Wednesday, and went even
OL,18,Ffurther by freezing the health element
OL,19,Fof universal credit to save extra cash.
