OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FWhen the package of benefits cuts was
OL,7,Fannounced last week, the government
OL,8,Fsaid they were waiting to publish
OL,9,Fdetails on how many people were
OL,10,Fimpacted until the Spring Statement.
OL,12,FCritics have accused the government of
OL,13,Ftrying to "bury bad news," as the
OL,14,Ffigures show the cuts will hit
OL,15,Fmillions of vulnerable families and
OL,16,Fdisabled people.
