OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FThe government estimates that in 2029-
OL,7,F30, 3.2 million families will lose an
OL,8,Faverage of #1,720 a year as a result
OL,9,Fof the cuts, with 250,000 people
OL,10,Fpushed into relative poverty.
