OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FThe impact assessment also shows that
OL,7,Fthe decision to tighten eligibility
OL,8,Ffor Personal Independence Payments
OL,9,F(Pip) will affect 800,000 disabled
OL,10,Fpeople who will lose an average of
OL,11,F#4,500 a year.
OL,13,FThat figure includes 370,000 current
OL,14,Frecipients and 430,000 future Pip
OL,15,Frecipients.
OL,17,FWork and Pensions Secretary Liz
OL,18,FKendall announced last week that fewer
OL,19,Fpeople will be eligible for Pip, with
OL,20,Fclaimants having to prove more severe
OL,21,Fdifficulties in order to qualify.
