OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FPip is a benefit designed to help
OL,7,Fpeople with a disability pay for
OL,8,Fadditional costs, such as wheelchairs,
OL,9,Fcars, above-average bills, carers, and
OL,10,Fspecialist equipment. The benefit can
OL,11,Fbe claimed by people both in and out
OL,12,Fof work and is not means-tested.
OL,14,FOn Wednesday, Reeves announced she was
OL,15,Fgoing further in her cuts to the
OL,16,Fhealth element of universal credit,
OL,17,Fwith an already announced cut of 50%
OL,18,Fbeing followed by a freeze on the rate
OL,19,Fof payments until 2030.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
