OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FThe health element of universal credit
OL,7,Fis a separate benefit to Pip, which
OL,8,Fcan be claimed if you can't work
OL,9,Fbecause of sickness or disability.
OL,11,FThe chancellor also announced the
OL,12,Funiversal credit standard allowance
OL,13,Fwill now increase from #92 per week in
OL,14,F2025-26 to #106 per week by 2029-30.
OL,16,FThe government expects 2.25 million
OL,17,Fpeople who claim the health element of
OL,18,Funiversal credit to be impacted by the
OL,19,Ffreeze, with an average loss of #500 a
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
