OL,3,CHow many people will be hit by Reeves'
OL,4,Cwelfare cuts?
OL,6,FOn top of that, 730,000 future
OL,7,Frecipients will be hit, with an
OL,8,Faverage loss of #3,000 a year.
OL,10,FDespite that, the government says 3.9
OL,11,Fmillion households on universal
OL,12,Fcredit, but not the health element of
OL,13,Fit will gain an average of #265 a year.
OL,15,FOn top of the above sums, the
OL,16,Fgovernment insists its #1 billion a
OL,17,Fyear investment into employment
OL,18,Fsupport for disabled and long-term
OL,19,Fsick people will "mitigate" the impact
OL,20,Fof the cuts.
