OL,6,FDavey said: "These cuts will be a
OL,7,Fdouble whammy to the most vulnerable,
OL,8,Fhitting disabled people who cannot
OL,9,Fwork while slashing support for the
OL,10,Floved ones who care for them.
OL,12,F"Carers need more support, not less.
OL,13,FSnatching away the little support
OL,14,Fthese carers get will do nothing to
OL,15,Fhelp people into work; it will just
OL,16,Fput more pressure on already over-
OL,17,Fstretched carers, social care and the
OL,18,FNHS.
